com.teamwork.autocomplete.view

Class SimpleItemViewBinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamwork.autocomplete.view.SimpleItemViewBinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCompleteViewBinder<SimpleItem>

    public class SimpleItemViewBinder
extends java.lang.Object
implements AutoCompleteViewBinder<SimpleItem>
    Item view binder for a SimpleItem model.

    It provides very basic behaviour for components that don't need any customization:

    • getItemId(SimpleItem) returns the item's hash code
    • It binds the data to the R.layout.simple_item layout
    • It highlights the portion of text that matches the current text constraint
    To prevent the library to have dependencies on any image loading/caching framework, images are not loaded into the image view. To implement your own loading, override onImageViewBind(ImageView, SimpleItem).
